			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Just like the subject says.  I am thinking very serious about 3-boxing.  The 3rd account would not have it's own computer, but be ran as a 2nd instance from my fastest computer.
<br />

<br />
I have got the 2-box thing with bard and Necro down well.  I can win 65% my of LDoNs.  I need a little more DPS.  I have a 3rd account available to me now.  I may make a new character to join this team.
<br />

<br />
I will of course need something that needs very little attention, so I was leaning toward Beastlord or Mage.
<br />

<br />
I'm thinking the Beastlord would be nice for slows and heals and someone else for the mobs to beat on now and then.  The BL pet is good.
<br />

<br />
Mage has nukes, pet toys and other summoned stuff, a great pet and CoH.  But, as a caster he would tend to be a bit fragile.  An advantage is that there is a 30th lvl mage already on the account.
<br />

<br />
Any opinions?  Other suggestions?<br />_________________<br />I love deadlines.  I love the whooshing sound they make as they fly by.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
