			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">/pause x,/cast y
<br />

<br />
Nit pick.. but.. the pause happens after the cast (yes.. it's weird, but it does).
<br />

<br />
So something like:
<br />

<br />
/pause 2,/assist MA 
<br />
/pet attack 
<br />
/pause 20,/cast 3 
<br />
/pause 30,/cast 4 
<br />
/cast 5 
<br />

<br />
But.. then you are locked in for the length of the macro.  I just make single keys like:
<br />

<br />
1: assist me
<br />
2: pet attack
<br />
3: pet hold
<br />
4: pet back
<br />
5: nuke 1
<br />
6: nuke 2
<br />

<br />
and mash them as I toggle through that session (re: previous post)</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
